# NFT Lions

A new series of unique NFTS 100 Lions each one is a 1 of 1 NFT with unlockables, including a 3D OBJ File.

Once purchased you can create derivatives of your lion for secondary markets, or to grow your pride whilst also gain access to the NFT Jungle futures. 

With future unlockables and future events when the world unlocks, each piece has been created with love and a unique story with superpowers.

The Lions are exclusive to OpenSea.io currently and are on the Etherium BlockChain, currently working with the metamask wallet & priced in etherium.

Prices are dependent on Powers & Accessories Prices will start from 0.1 eth and will vary but prices will only ever go up.
